<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>PHP's fileinfo-Extension has the possibility to take your own Magic-File for MimeType-Determination. In ZF you "can" do this, by setting the magicFile-Option.</p>

<p>The setOptions-Method of Zend_Transfer_Adapter_Abstract converts every setting to bool (Line 554 in recent trunk). This is right for 'ignoreNoFile' or 'useByteString', but not for magicFile.</p>

<p>$this-&gt;_files[$key]['options'][$name] = (boolean) $value;</p>

<p>Due to this, you can't use you own magicFile!</p>

